quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  70,19,Beshak insan baray kachy dil wala banaya gaya hay
  70,20,Jab is say musibat puhanchti hay to har bara uthta hay
  70,21,aur jab rahat milti hay to bukhul kernay lagta hay
  70,22,Mager wo namazi
  70,23,J apnai namaz per hameshagi kernay walay hein
  70,24,Aur jin kay maalon mein mukarra hisa hay
  70,25,Mangnay walon ka bhi aur sawal say bachnay walon ka bhi
  70,26,Aur jo insaf kay din per yaqeen rakhtay hein
  70,27,Aur jo apney rab kay azab say dertay rehtay hein
  70,28,Beshak un kay rab ka azab bekhof honay ki chez nahi
  70,29,Aur jo log apni sharm gahon ki (haram say)hifazat kertay hein
  70,30,Han unki biwion aur londion kay bary mein jin kay wo malik hein.unhein koi malamat nahi
  70,31,Ab jo koi is kay ilawa(rah)dhonday ga to asay log had say guzar janay walay hongay
  70,32,Aur jo apni amanton ka aur apney qol o qarar ka pass rakhtay hein
  70,33,Aur jo apni gawahion per sidhay aur qaim rehtay hein
  70,34,Aur jo apni namazon ki hifazat kertay hein
  70,35,Yehi log janton mein izat walay hongay
  70,36,Pus kafoiron ko kia hogaya hay kay wo teri taraf dortay atay hein
  70,37,Daein aur baein say giroh kay giroh
  70,38,Kia in mein say her ik ki tawaqa yeh hay kay wo nematon wali janat mein dakhil kia jaey ga
  70,39,(aisa) hergiz nahi ho ga hum ney unhein is(chez) say paida kia hay jiss say wo jantay hein
  70,40,Pus mujhy qasam hay mashrikon aur maghribon kay rab ki (kay)hum yaqeenan qadir hein
  70,41,Is per kay in kay ewaz in say achay log lay ayein aur hum aajiz nahi hein
  70,42,Pus to inhein jagherta khelata chor day yahan ytak kay yeh apney us din say jamilein jis ka un say wada kia jata hay
  70,43,Jis din yeh qabron say dortay hoy niklein gay goya kay wo kisi jaga ki taraf tez tez jarahy hein
  70,44,In ki ankhein jhoki hoi hongi in per zilat charahi hon gi yeh hay wo din jis ka un say wada kia jata tha
  71,1,Yaqeenan hum ney Nooh(alh e salam)ko inki qom ki taraf bheja kay apni qom ko darado (aur khabaerdar kerdo) isss say pehlay kay inkay pass dardnak azab ajaye
  71,2,(Nooh alh e salam ney)kaha aey meri qom mein tumhein saaf saaf daranay wala hun
  71,3,Kay tum Allah ki ibadat kero aur issi say daro aur mera kaha maano
  71,4,To wo tumhary gunha bukhsh day ga aur tumhein aik waqat mukarrera tak chor dega YaqeenanAllah ka wada jab aajata hay to moakhir nahi hota kaash kay tumhien samjh hoti
  71,5,(nooh alh e salam ney) kaha aey mery perwardigar!mein ney apni qom ko raat din teri taraf bulaya hai
  71,6,Mager meray bulanay say yeh log aur ziyada bhagnay lagay
  71,7,Mein ney jab khabi unhein teri bakhsish kay liye bulaya unhon ney apni ungliyan apney kaano mein daal lein aur apney kapron ko orh liya aur urh gaye aur bara takabur kiya
  71,8,Phir mein ney unhein ba-awaz buland bulaya
  71,9,Aur beshak mein ney insay elaaniya bhi kaha aur chupkay chupkay bhi
  71,10,Aur mein ney kaha kay apney rab say apney gunha bakhswao(aur maafi mango)wo yaqeenan bara bakhsnay wala hay
  71,11,Wo tum per aasman ko khob barsata hua chor dega
  71,12,Aur tumhein khob pay dar pay maal aur olaad mein taraqi dega Aur tumhein baaghat dega aur tumharay liye nikaal dega
  71,13,Tumhein kiya hogaya hay kay tum Allah ki bartari ki aqeedah nahi rakhtay
  71,14,Halankay uss ney tumhein tarah tarah say paida kiya hay
  71,15,Kiya tum nahi dekhtay kay Allah Talah ney kiss tarah opper talay sath asman paida ker diey hein
  71,16,Aur in mien chand ko khob jagmata banaya hai aur sooraj ko roshan chiragh banaya hay
  71,17,Aur tum ko zameen say aik (khass ehtimam say)ugaya hai(aur paida kiya hai)
  71,18,Phir tumhein issi mein lota leya jaeyga aur(aik khass tareeqay)say phir nikalay ga
  71,19,Aur tumharay liye zameen ko Allah Taalaa ney farsh banadiya hay
  71,20,Takay tum uski kushada raahon mein chalo phiro
  71,21,Nooh(alh e salam) ney kaha aey meray perwardigar!in logon ney meri to nafarmani ki aur aison ki farmanbardari ki jinkay maal o olaad ney inko(yaqeenan)nuksan hi mein barhaya hai
  71,22,Aur in logon ney bara sakht fareeb kiya
  71,23,Aur kaha unhon ney kay hergiz apney maaboodon ko na chorna aur na wad aur suwaa aur yaghoos aur yaooq aur nasar ko(chorna)
  71,24,Aur unhon ney bohat say logon ko gumrah kiya (elaahi)tu in zaalimon ki gumrahi aur barha
  71,25,Yeh log ba sabab apney gunaahon kay dabo deygay aur jahanum mein phuncha diey gaye aur Allah kay siwa apna koi madadgar unhonay na paya
  71,26,Aur Nooh(alh e salam)ney kaha kay aey mery paalnay walay! To roy e zameen per kissi kafir ko rehnay sehnay wala na chor
  71,27,Ager to enhen chor dega to (yaqeenan)yeh tery (aur)bandon ko(bhi)gumrah kardeingay aur yeh faajiron aur dheet kafiron hi ko janum deingay
  71,28,Aey meray perwardigar!to mujhay aur meray maa baap aur jo eman ki halat mein meray ghar +mein aye aur tamam momin mardon aur auraton ko bakhsh dey aur kafiron ko siwaey barbadi key aur kissi baat mein na barha